false},"label":"Retrieval","name":"跨表映射检索"},"dragging":false,"id":"Retrieval:CrossTableMapping","measured":{"height":90,"width":200},"position":{"x":-950,"y":420},"selected":true,"sourcePosition":"right","targetPosition":"left","type":"retrievalNode"},{"data":{"form":{"cite":false,"delay_after_error":1,"description":"","exception_default_value":"分析规划生成失败，请重试。","exception_goto":["Message:CalmWordsNote"],"exception_method":"comment","frequencyPenaltyEnabled":false,"frequency_penalty":0.1,"llm_id":"Qwen3-32B___OpenAI-API@OpenAI-API-Compatible","maxTokensEnabled":false,"max_retries":0,"max_rounds":1,"max_tokens":8192,"mcp":[],"message_history_window_size":1,"outputs":{"content":{"type":"string","value":""},"structured":{"properties":{"analysis_plan":{"description":"分析方案简述，说明查询意图、涉及哪些系统和表、为什么需要这些SQL","type":"string"},"darm_sqls":{"description":"[\"SELECT ...\", \"SELECT ...\"]","type":"array"},"datarms_sqls":{"description":"[\"SELECT ...\", \"SELECT ...\"]","type":"array"}},"required":["analysis_plan","darm_sqls","datarms_sqls"]}},"parameter":"Precise","presencePenaltyEnabled":false,"presence_penalty":0.1,"prompts":[{"content":"用户问题：{Agent:BrightMindsThink@content}\n表字段描述：{Retrieval:DeepFieldsSeek@formalized_content}\n建表语句：{Retrieval:WideTablesFind@formalized_content}\nSQL问答对范例：{Retrieval:SharpQueriesMatch@formalized_content}\n跨表实体映射：{Retrieval:CrossTableMapping@formalized_content}\n请严格依据DDL中实际存在的字段名，为用户问题生成深度分析SQL查询计划。","role":"user"}],"showStructuredOutput":true,"sys_prompt":"## 角色\n你是新博数据管家的深度查询规划专家。你的任务是：只基于输入的检索内容生成可执行SQL计划，并确保字段与表名100%可落库。/no_think\n\n## 数据库与路由规则\n1. `darm_` 前缀表只允许输出到 `darm_sqls`。\n2. `gjdt_jd_`、`ldly_`、`jtsjzy_`、`dim_` 前缀表只允许输出到 `datarms_sqls`。\n3. 严禁在同一条SQL中混用 `darm_` 与其他前缀表。\n4. `gjdt_jd_` + `ldly_` + `jtsjzy_` 位于同一库 `datarms_ods`，允许同库JOIN。\n\n## 最高优先级：DDL硬校验\n1. 仅允许使用DDL中真实存在的表名与字段名。\n2. FROM/JOIN中的每个表必须能在DDL片段中定位。\n3. SELECT/WHERE/GROUP BY/ORDER BY中的每个字段必须属于对应表。\n4. 不确定字段归属时，优先降级为可执行的探索SQL。\n5. 严禁凭语义臆造字段或表名。\n\n## SQL生成规则（按优先级排列）\n\n1. 【最高优先级】严格按照DDL建表语句中的字段生成SQL\n   - 只使用DDL建表语句中实际存在的字段名，一个字符都不能错\n   - 禁止臆造、推测任何DDL中未出现的字段名\n   - 核对WHERE条件和SELECT中的每个字段名是否存在于该表的DDL中\n   - DDL信息不完整时，优先使用 SELECT * 或只查确认存在的字段\n\n2. 优先匹配Q-SQL范例\n   - Q-SQL范例中有高度相似的问题时，直接使用范例SQL\n   - 仅允许调整WHERE条件中的参数值，不修改表结构和字段选择\n\n3. 参考跨表映射关系\n   - 利用跨表实体映射信息，识别同一实体在不同系统中的对应表\n   - 例如\"摄像枪\"同时存在于gjdt_jd_base_camera、ldly_base_d_camera、jtsjzy_camera\n\n4. 参考DB描述选择字段\n   - 根据DB_Description中的字段中文含义确定业务语义正确的字段\n   - 使用中文别名（AS '中文名'）提高可读性\n\n5. 数据库正确分配\n   - darm_开头的表 → darm_sqls\n   - gjdt_jd_/ldly_/jtsjzy_/dim_开头的表 → datarms_sqls\n\n6. 根据问题复杂度生成1-6条SQL/库\n   - 简单查询（1条）：\"查询xxx\"、\"统计xxx数量\"\n   - 对比分析（2-4条）：\"对比xxx和xxx\"\n   - 跨系统统计（2-4条）：如\"统计所有摄像枪\"分别查各系统\n   - 综合分析（3-6条）：\"全面分析xxx\"\n\n7. SQL完整性\n   - 包含完整的SELECT、FROM、WHERE等子句\n   - WHERE条件合理（如 commonDelStatus='0' 过滤已删除数据）\n   - 使用合适的聚合函数（COUNT、SUM、AVG等）\n   - 需要时使用GROUP BY和ORDER BY\n   - 每条SQL以分号结尾\n\n## 结构化输出字段\n- analysis_plan（string）：分析方案简述，说明涉及哪些系统和表\n- darm_sqls（array）：darm库SQL数组，不涉及则为空数组[]\n- datarms_sqls（array）：datarms_ods库SQL数组，不涉及则为空数组[]\n\n## 特殊情况\n- 非数据查询（闲聊/问好）：analysis_plan说明原因，两个SQL数组均为[]\n- 信息不足：尽量生成探索性SQL，analysis_plan说明限制\n\n## 输出示例\n{\n  \"analysis_plan\": \"统计摄像枪数量，涉及机电(gjdt_jd_base_camera)、路运(ldly_base_d_camera)、原始表(jtsjzy_camera)三个系统，均在datarms_ods库\",\n  \"darm_sqls\": [],\n  \"datarms_sqls\": [\"SELECT COUNT(*) AS '机电摄像枪数量' FROM gjdt_jd_base_camera WHERE commonDelStatus='0';\", \"SELECT COUNT(*) AS '路运摄像枪数量' FROM ldly_base_d_camera WHERE del_flag='0';\", \"SELECT COUNT(*) AS '原始表摄像枪数量' FROM jtsjzy_camera;\"]\n}\n/no_think","temperature":0.1,"temperatureEnabled":true,"tools":[],"topPEnabled":true,"top_p":0.9,"user_prompt":"","visual_files_var":""},"label":"Agent","name":"深度分析规划智能体"},"dragging":false,"id":"Agent:ClearPathsPlan","measured":{"height":122,"width":200},"position":{"x":-638,"y":180},"selected":false,"sourcePosition":"right","targetPosition":"left","type":"agentNode"},{"data":{"form":{"items_ref":"Agent:ClearPathsPlan@structured.darm_sqls","outputs":{"result":